review 1: When we talk about farming in Bali, we talk about Life! That what we learn here at the UMAWALI Community. We really support their work and effort to build the movement of sustainable and healthy farming system in Bali.
review 2: A good experience if you are looking for non commercial attraction who give u great scenery, knowledge, Bali culture and different feeling about Bali. A must go destination if you want to know the real Balinese. Sincere villagers will melt ur heart
review 3:
A must go place in Bali if you want your kid to experience real natural village in Bali.

The village is the embodiment of natural sustainable and healthy farming system in Bali. They don't even want to commercialize the village.
review 4: Beautiful village, humble villagers and great conservation
